<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-04-23T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-04-23T13:00:00-05:00" n="373" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d373">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51W89 Czechoslovakia/175a:
                                Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Minister in Czechoslovakia (<persName type="to">Ratshesky</persName>)</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-04-23T13:00:00-05:00">April
                                        23, 1932—1 p.m.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>15. Treasury draft of agreement to carry out Congressional Resolution
                                regarding debt postponement was handed to Czechoslovakian Minister
                                some time ago. Treasury insists on necessity of quick action in view
                                of June 15th payment date approaching. Please discuss present
                                situation with appropriate authorities and inquire when action may
                                be expected, reporting fully.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_CWR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>